Type: Package
Package: ffscrapr
Title: ffscrapr - R Client For Fantasy Football League Platforms
Version: 0.0.4.22
URL: https://ffscrapr.dynastyprocess.com, https://github.com/dynastyprocess/ffscrapr
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Tan",
           family = "Ho",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "tan@tanho.ca")
Description: Helps access various Fantasy Football APIs (i.e. MFL, Sleeper, Fleaflicker, ESPN, Yahoo) 
    by handling authentication and rate-limiting, forming appropriate calls, 
    and returning tidy dataframes which can be easily connected to other data sources.
